were meant to be

56
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,840
two pieces of a single stone.

57
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,160
You would have been
perfect for each other,

58
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,320
but

59
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,040
your life span is over.

60
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,120
You two

61
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,600
are not just linked by marriage,

62
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,200
