69
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:05,960
Her fainting

70
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,240
just now

71
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,600
was one of the signs.

72
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,560
Break the spell.

73
